{"tid":715951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8歲女童天生無腳，只能以沙甸魚罐頭充當義肢！","createTime":"2018-06-25T01:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T02:47:42.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"315b395ead4412c6e114842994774c00a1806156","tid":715951,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T01:18:48.000Z","msg":"有片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3wP_VY-H2Z4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3wP_VY-H2Z4&d=KGDUDqk4DuKEzo%2Bg3B1nH%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=1d8bd118\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3wP_VY-H2Z4</a><br />\n<br />\n敍利亞飽受戰亂摧殘，無辜民眾為了躲避戰火逃離家園（圖）前往難民營。一名8歲女童瑪雅（Maya Mohammad Ali Merhi）天生沒有小腿，在資源匱乏的難民營中，只能夠用兩個沙甸魚罐頭充當義肢，在沙地上慢慢行走，見者心酸。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpkOjYCk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpkOjYCk.jpg&h=893d2720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">瑪雅天生沒有雙腿。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n其父說：「望着她在爬，而其他人又跑又玩時，真是心如刀割。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180625/20430547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F20430547&d=KGDUDqk4DuKEzo%2Bg3B1nH%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=4d31511d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F20430547&h=84feb4f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180625/20430547</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_news/敘8歲童先天無下肢-罐頭塞棉花充當義肢/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fmetro_news%2F%E6%95%988%E6%AD%B2%E7%AB%A5%E5%85%88%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%A1%E4%B8%8B%E8%82%A2-%E7%BD%90%E9